615
00:56:28,490 --> 00:56:31,994
And I so apologize, but he didn't want to say, come back.

616
00:56:32,295 --> 00:56:40,105
And I didn't want to say to all of you, but full disclosure, it was one timing error that I profusely apologize for.

617
00:56:40,125 --> 00:56:41,807
I am sorry.

618
00:56:44,412 --> 00:56:45,152
Okay, good.

619
00:56:45,292 --> 00:56:45,653
Thank you.

620
00:56:45,693 --> 00:56:46,673
But I did want to say that.

621
00:56:47,013 --> 00:56:49,114
So thanks everybody for coming.

622
00:56:49,194 --> 00:56:53,015
I think it's such a great turnout and I think we have a wonderful pool of candidates.

623
00:56:53,656 --> 00:56:55,796
And I say, Bruce, would you like to say anything?

624
00:56:56,917 --> 00:56:57,477
We're all set.

625
00:56:57,537 --> 00:56:58,517
Thank you all for coming.

